Grammar

    0 $accept: line_list $end

    1 line_list: line
    2          | line_list line

    3 line: definition END CR

    4 definition: TYPE VAR
    5           | TYPE VAR '=' NUM
    6           | TYPE VAR '=' FLOAT_LIT
    7           | TYPE VAR '=' CHAR_LIT
    8           | TYPE VAR '=' STRING_LIT
    9           | TYPE VAR '=' DOUBLE_LIT


Terminals, with rules where they appear

    $end (0) 0
    '=' (61) 5 6 7 8 9
    error (256)
    NUM (258) 5
    VAR (259) 4 5 6 7 8 9
    CR (260) 3
    TYPE (261) 4 5 6 7 8 9
    END (262) 3
    FLOAT_LIT (263) 6
    CHAR_LIT (264) 7
    STRING_LIT (265) 8
    DOUBLE_LIT (266) 9


Nonterminals, with rules where they appear

    $accept (13)
        on left: 0
    line_list (14)
        on left: 1 2
        on right: 0 2
    line (15)
        on left: 3
        on right: 1 2
    definition (16)
        on left: 4 5 6 7 8 9
        on right: 3


State 0

    0 $accept: . line_list $end

    TYPE  shift, and go to state 1

    line_list   go to state 2
    line        go to state 3
    definition  go to state 4


State 1

    4 definition: TYPE . VAR
    5           | TYPE . VAR '=' NUM
    6           | TYPE . VAR '=' FLOAT_LIT
    7           | TYPE . VAR '=' CHAR_LIT
    8           | TYPE . VAR '=' STRING_LIT
    9           | TYPE . VAR '=' DOUBLE_LIT

    VAR  shift, and go to state 5


State 2

    0 $accept: line_list . $end
    2 line_list: line_list . line

    $end  shift, and go to state 6
    TYPE  shift, and go to state 1

    line        go to state 7
    definition  go to state 4


State 3

    1 line_list: line .

    $default  reduce using rule 1 (line_list)


State 4

    3 line: definition . END CR

    END  shift, and go to state 8


State 5

    4 definition: TYPE VAR .
    5           | TYPE VAR . '=' NUM
    6           | TYPE VAR . '=' FLOAT_LIT
    7           | TYPE VAR . '=' CHAR_LIT
    8           | TYPE VAR . '=' STRING_LIT
    9           | TYPE VAR . '=' DOUBLE_LIT

    '='  shift, and go to state 9

    $default  reduce using rule 4 (definition)


State 6

    0 $accept: line_list $end .

    $default  accept


State 7

    2 line_list: line_list line .

    $default  reduce using rule 2 (line_list)


State 8

    3 line: definition END . CR

    CR  shift, and go to state 10


State 9

    5 definition: TYPE VAR '=' . NUM
    6           | TYPE VAR '=' . FLOAT_LIT
    7           | TYPE VAR '=' . CHAR_LIT
    8           | TYPE VAR '=' . STRING_LIT
    9           | TYPE VAR '=' . DOUBLE_LIT

    NUM         shift, and go to state 11
    FLOAT_LIT   shift, and go to state 12
    CHAR_LIT    shift, and go to state 13
    STRING_LIT  shift, and go to state 14
    DOUBLE_LIT  shift, and go to state 15


State 10

    3 line: definition END CR .

    $default  reduce using rule 3 (line)


State 11

    5 definition: TYPE VAR '=' NUM .

    $default  reduce using rule 5 (definition)


State 12

    6 definition: TYPE VAR '=' FLOAT_LIT .

    $default  reduce using rule 6 (definition)


State 13

    7 definition: TYPE VAR '=' CHAR_LIT .

    $default  reduce using rule 7 (definition)


State 14

    8 definition: TYPE VAR '=' STRING_LIT .

    $default  reduce using rule 8 (definition)


State 15

    9 definition: TYPE VAR '=' DOUBLE_LIT .

    $default  reduce using rule 9 (definition)
